text: Azim Khan (born 15 September 1999) is an Afghan cricketer. He made his List A debut for Balkh Province in the 2019 Afghanistan Provincial Challenge Cup tournament on 1 August 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Afghan cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
